snippet.title: THE EDCO INCIDENT Full Game Walkthrough (No Commentary) (Indie Horror Game 2019)
snippet.description:
Feel free to Like and Subscribe!

The EdCo Incident is a PowerPoint Horror game I spent nearly two and a half years on. Since not everyone has a device that can run PowerPoint, I thought I'd upload a no commentary full game walkthrough. Enjoy!

Check out some of my teaser trailers for the game! 

Newest Trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gyZWYvFqA20

Second Trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XGjoAxKnFJs

Original Trailer:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2-ImXU-tAkk
